headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Simeon Missions
content: Simeon Yetarian has been called many things, most of them unsavory, but one thing he is for sure is enterprising. If the mogul of Premium Deluxe Motorsport contacts you for help with a couple recoupments and repossessions, take him up on his offer – he’s paying out 2X GTA$ and RP to all takers on Missions and Premium Deluxe Repo Work.
